collections.name: Kiwanoid Music Collection
collections.description: Difficult-to-define sound environment somewhere between sound art, sound sculpture, conceptual art and post-techno. It operates directly with the states of consciousness and the zones of perception. According to the audible, it can be assumed that there are basically all kinds of machines in this environment. Some of them are old, big and capable, and drowsily-buzzing, while others are small, modern, dependable and electronic, subtly tweeting. And the third type, which operate at a relatively unobtrusive distance, are modestly functional and smooth, but are irresistibly skilled techno-conveyors. At the same time, not all of these machines work as haphazardly and spontaneously, but leave behind an inaccessible, mystical organization on the other side of good and evil, order and chaos, the enigmatic patterns of technopaganism, and the sterile digital minimalism of glitch conceptualism.

collections.name: Goryeo Buddhist Painting
collections.description:
고려불화  – 수월관음도
이 NFT는 고려불화 ‘수월관음도’를 현대적인 디지털 기술과 결합하여 재해석한 작품입니다.  
나는 전생에서 수행자로 살았고, 지금은 붓을 들어 수행을 이어가고 있습니다.  
내게 고려불화를 그리는 것은.  
한 획 한 획 긋는 과정 속에서, 나는 전생의 기억을 떠올리고,  
윤회의 흐름 속에서 인간의 삶을 그려 나갑니다.  

수월관음도(水月觀音圖)는 **물과 달이 비추는 듯한 관음보살의 모습**을 담고 있습니다.  
이는 불교에서 말하는 **공(空)의 진리, 마음의 고요함, 수행을 통한 깨달음**을 상징하며,  
고려불화 특유의 섬세한 채색과 우아한 선을 통해 신비로운 분위기를 자아냅니다.  

이 NFT는
수행과 윤회, 그리고 인간의 깨달음을 형상화한 작품이며,  
**단 20개만 발행된 한정판 NFT**입니다.  

제 그림의 소유자 들은   
전통미술 계승의 가치를 함께하는 후원자가 될것입니다.

This NFT is a modern reinterpretation of "Water-Moon Avalokiteshvara",
a masterpiece of Goryeo Buddhist painting, blending traditional techniques with digital art.

In my past life, I lived as a monk, devoted to spiritual practice.
Now, in this life, I continue my practice through my brush.
For me, painting Goryeo Buddhist art is not merely an artistic endeavor.

With each stroke, I recall the memories of my past life,
and within the cycle of reincarnation, I depict the essence of human existence.

The Water-Moon Avalokites

collections.name: Emberfall Artisans
collections.description: "Emberfall Artisans" is a captivating NFT collection of 6,222 unique tokens, inspired by the fiery craftsmanship of a mythical volcanic land known as Emberfall. Each token features a randomly generated Artisan—a skilled creator wielding molten tools, ember-infused jewelry, and ash-dusted robes. From lava forgers shaping radiant blades to ash weavers crafting smoldering tapestries, every character embodies the raw power and beauty of volcanic artistry. The collection blends fiery aesthetics with artisanal mastery, with 1.3% of tokens designated as "Volcanic Masters," distinguished by animated ember pulses and obsidian-crimson accents. Collectors gain access to virtual forge workshops and a share of 6.5% royalties from secondary sales, inviting them to craft their legacy in the heart of the flames.
